SELECT "bill_length", "bill_depth" FROM "penguins" AS "source"

SELECT "i" AS "index", SUM("w")::DOUBLE AS "density" FROM (SELECT ("time"::DOUBLE - 0.01666666753590107) * 13.643949786176242::DOUBLE AS "xp", ("delay"::DOUBLE - -58) * 0.9201680672268907::DOUBLE AS "yp", FLOOR(xp)::INTEGER + FLOOR(yp)::INTEGER * 328 AS "i", (FLOOR(xp)::INTEGER + 1 - xp) * (FLOOR(yp)::INTEGER + 1 - yp) AS "w" FROM "flights" WHERE ("time" BETWEEN 0.01666666753590107 AND 23.983333587646484) AND ("delay" BETWEEN -58 AND 180) UNION ALL SELECT ("time"::DOUBLE - 0.01666666753590107) * 13.643949786176242::DOUBLE AS "xp", ("delay"::DOUBLE - -58) * 0.9201680672268907::DOUBLE AS "yp", FLOOR(xp)::INTEGER + (FLOOR(yp)::INTEGER + 1) * 328 AS "i", (FLOOR(xp)::INTEGER + 1 - xp) * (yp - FLOOR(yp)::INTEGER) AS "w" FROM "flights" WHERE ("time" BETWEEN 0.01666666753590107 AND 23.983333587646484) AND ("delay" BETWEEN -58 AND 180) UNION ALL SELECT ("time"::DOUBLE - 0.01666666753590107) * 13.643949786176242::DOUBLE AS "xp", ("delay"::DOUBLE - -58) * 0.9201680672268907::DOUBLE AS "yp", FLOOR(xp)::INTEGER + 1 + FLOOR(yp)::INTEGER * 328 AS "i", (xp - FLOOR(xp)::INTEGER) * (FLOOR(yp)::INTEGER + 1 - yp) AS "w" FROM "flights" WHERE ("time" BETWEEN 0.01666666753590107 AND 23.983333587646484) AND ("delay" BETWEEN -58 AND 180) UNION ALL SELECT ("time"::DOUBLE - 0.01666666753590107) * 13.643949786176242::DOUBLE AS "xp", ("delay"::DOUBLE - -58) * 0.9201680672268907::DOUBLE AS "yp", FLOOR(xp)::INTEGER + 1 + (FLOOR(yp)::INTEGER + 1) * 328 AS "i", (xp - FLOOR(xp)::INTEGER) * (yp - FLOOR(yp)::INTEGER) AS "w" FROM "flights" WHERE ("time" BETWEEN 0.01666666753590107 AND 23.983333587646484) AND ("delay" BETWEEN -58 AND 180)) GROUP BY "index" HAVING ("density" <> 0)
